Description.Name: Precision AC/5 Ammo
Description.Details:
Ammo Bins contain the rounds needed for projectile-based weaponry, with at least one bin required per weapon type. Ammo Bins will explode and destroy their installed location when they receive a Critical Hit.

Precision rounds use a gyrojet shell that can correct its course in mid-flight, making them especially effective against fast targets, but also increases the mass of each shell. Precision AC/5 Ammo Bins contain only 8 rounds and can only be used in standard and light autocannons.
